column16: Alexei Ramirez grounds out softly, third baseman Chase Headley to first baseman Mark Teixeira.
Derek Norris pops out to shortstop Didi Gregorius in foul territory.
Melvin Upton Jr.   strikes out swinging.
Adrian Beltre flies out to center fielder Jacoby Ellsbury.
Nick Ahmed grounds into a force out, third baseman Chase Headley to second baseman Starlin Castro.   Chris Herrmann out at 2nd.
Chris Herrmann walks.   Michael Bourn scores.    Yasmany Tomas to 3rd.    Brandon Drury to 2nd.
Brandon Drury hit by pitch.    Yasmany Tomas to 2nd.
Yasmany Tomas grounds into a force out, shortstop Didi Gregorius to second baseman Starlin Castro.   Michael Bourn to 3rd.    Jake Lamb out at 2nd.    Yasmany Tomas to 1st.
